GrantId.description: Unique identifier of the grant to retire. The grant ID is returned in the response to a CreateGrant operation.   Grant ID Example - 0123456789012345678901234567890123456789012345678901234567890123

GrantToken.description: Token that identifies the grant to be retired.

KeyId.description: The Amazon Resource Name of the CMK associated with the grant. Example:   arn:aws:kms:us-east-2:444455556666:key/1234abcd-12ab-34cd-56ef-1234567890ab
